%% E103 - Chat SSE flow sequence - F1-11 Frontend
%% Source: docs/design/f1-11-chat-ui.md (E102)
%% Note: API uses POST; client uses fetch + ReadableStream (EventSource is GET-only)
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant ChatView as ChatViewComponent
    participant ChatService
    participant API as ChatController

    User->>ChatView: Enter query, click Send
    ChatView->>ChatView: Add user message to list
    ChatView->>ChatService: sendMessage(query)
    ChatService->>API: POST /api/chat (body: query)
    API-->>ChatService: 200 OK, text/event-stream

    loop SSE chunks
        ChatService-->>ChatView: emit chunk (Observable)
        ChatView->>ChatView: Append chunk to assistant message
        ChatView->>ChatView: Parse citations {caso, id}
        ChatView->>ChatView: Render links (RouterLink to /fallos/:id)
        ChatView->>ChatView: Auto-scroll to bottom
    end

    ChatService-->>ChatView: stream complete
    ChatView->>ChatView: Mark message complete, remove cursor
    ChatView->>User: Display full response with links
